::Feline::

She looked at Zardus. "Hmm, a mission. Sounds important." She reached 
over and ran her hand down Zardus' shoulder. "I was, ah, wondering. 
Do you have anthing in mind for me?" she said in a low and breathy 
voice. "Nothing too dangerous I hope. I mean, if it is dangerous," 
she got up and stood behind DevilDuer while he was sitting. She ran 
her hands down his chest and back up to his shoulders."I'd have to 
ask for backup." She was smiling with a gleam in her eye. 
"After all, I am just a pussy cat." she stood up and sat back down in 
her own seat. She crossed her legs and looked at Zardus with a 
smile.  She blew him a kiss and purred.
